title: Son of a Boy Dad: Ep. 10 - The Art of Podcasting with BIG CAT
description:
-- Sas & Rone are joined by friend of the program Barstool Big Cat. We discuss fatherhood, playing pickup with Vaynerchuk, fist fights, responding to the right DMs, & much more. -- Make sure to check out our new merch as well!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/sonofaboydad
